This paper involves the use of deep learning algorithms to analyze fundus images for the detection of glaucoma, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the analysis of medical images for the detection of a specific disease, which falls under the category of medical imaging (cs.MED) and information retrieval (cs.IR) for the retrieval of relevant images.
